Silloway & Vaile...UWSP got 10 points & 10 rebounds from Collins...Teams
missed all 11 3-point shots in first quarter...UWSP had 25 turnovers...UWO
jumped to 17-7 lead...UWO clinched at least a share of WIAC East title.
